IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User pranomestro
PassCmd "spm show pranomestro@gmail"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Inbox "/usr/local/mail/gmail/INBOX/"
Path "/usr/local/mail/gmail/"

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
User pranomostro@posteo.net
AuthMechs LOGIN
PassCmd "spm show pranomostro@posteo"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/posteo.crt

IMAPSTore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Inbox "/usr/local/mail/posteo/INBOX/"
Path "/usr/local/mail/posteo/"

Channel posteo
Master :posteo-remote:
Slave :posteo-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
